By Jessica Roy, 
The Mockingjay is not a member of Team Trump! 
In an interview with Entertainment Weekly , Jennifer Lawrence said, "If Donald Trump becomes president, that will be the end of the world." 
She expressed hope that it was all some freakish publicity stunt: "I genuinely believe that reality television has reached the ultimate place where now even things like this might just be for entertainment. ... It's either that or it's Hillary [Clinton]'s brilliant idea." 
Fall popularity contest: Vote on your favorite new shows now! 
If it is a publicity thing, perhaps everyone is in on it: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay Part 2 comes out next month, and between his hair and general behavior, Trump definitely seems like he could be a resident of the Capitol. Maybe he'll make a cameo as President Snow's VP?
